Class BaseFileSystemProvider<P extends BasePath<P>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.nio.file.spi.FileSystemProvider
      • com.palantir.giraffe.file.base.BaseFileSystemProvider<P>
  • Type Parameters:
    P - the type of path used by the provider's file systems
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    CachingBaseFileSystemProvider

    public abstract class BaseFileSystemProvider<P extends BasePath<P>>
extends FileSystemProvider
    An abstract FileSystemProvider implementation that provides common functionality and additional structure for subclasses.
